### Anamnesis Endpoints Test
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000/api

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@authToken = your_auth_token_here
@patientId = 1
@caregiverId = 1

### List all anamnesis
GET {{baseUrl}}/anamnesis/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Create anamnesis
POST {{baseUrl}}/anamnesis/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "patient": {{patientId}},
    "caregiver": {{caregiverId}},
    "main_diagnosis": "Transtorno do Espectro Autista",
    "associated_conditions": "TDAH, Ansiedade",
    "allergies": "Não possui alergias conhecidas",
    "medications": "Ritalina 10mg - 1x ao dia",
    "communication_methods": "Pictogramas, gestos, algumas palavras",
    "spoken_words": "Mamã, papá, água, banheiro",
    "preferred_pictograms": "Símbolos de comida, ações básicas",
    "dietary_restrictions": "Sem glúten",
    "food_preferences": "Frutas, massas",
    "feeding_difficulties": "Recusa alimentos com texturas diferentes",
    "needs_expression": "Aponta para objetos, usa pictogramas",
    "frustration_reactions": "Gritos, choro, movimentos repetitivos",
    "general_observations": "Criança muito carinhosa, gosta de rotina"
}

###

### Get specific anamnesis
GET {{baseUrl}}/anamnesis/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

